The biggest advantage of independent op-ed writersWe don't have editors. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-biggest-advantage-of-independent https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-biggest-advantage-of-independentNoah Smith Thu, 28 Mar 2024 07:48:50 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5d82dedc-b328-47e5-a3e6-1d383bef31ca_936x624.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5d82dedc-b328-47e5-a3e6-1d383bef31ca_936x624.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5d82dedc-b328-47e5-a3e6-1d383bef31ca_936x624.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5d82dedc-b328-47e5-a3e6-1d383bef31ca_936x624.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5d82dedc-b328-47e5-a3e6-1d383bef31ca_936x624.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5d82dedc-b328-47e5-a3e6-1d383bef31ca_936x624.jpeg" width="700" height="466.6666666666667" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5d82dedc-b328-47e5-a3e6-1d383bef31ca_936x624.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;f